            <span><strong>IKEA</strong> — Pindi has direct experience fitting IKEA METOD kitchens in Leamington's Victorian terraces. See the <a href="/retailers/ikea/" style="color: var(--teal);">IKEA installation page</a> and the <a href="/projects/ikea-kitchen-leamington-spa/" style="color: var(--teal);">Leamington Spa project</a>.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Wren Kitchens</strong> — one of the most popular choices across Warwickshire; Pindi fits Wren independently, without being tied to their installation scheme. See the <a href="/retailers/wren/" style="color: var(--teal);">Wren installation page</a>.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Howdens Joinery</strong> — Pindi holds a trade account with Howdens, giving him direct depot access. See the <a href="/retailers/howdens/" style="color: var(--teal);">Howdens installation page</a>.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Magnet</strong> — a common choice for Leamington homeowners seeking mid-range quality; all Magnet ranges are fully compatible with independent installation.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Wickes and B&amp;Q</strong> — both popular at accessible price points; Pindi brings the same attention to detail regardless of the kitchen's price point.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Benchmarx, DIY Kitchens, Kutchenhaus, Symphony, Masterclass</strong> — all covered as standard.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Premium and German brands</strong> — including Häcker, Nobilia, Mereway, Neptune and deVOL, regularly fitted in the larger detached properties across CV32 and Warwick.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          If your kitchen brand is not listed, call <a href="tel:07399651836" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">07399 651836</a> — in almost every case it can be accommodated.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <SupplierLogos />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Areas Covered -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Areas of Leamington Spa and South Warwickshire Covered
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Pindi covers the whole of Royal Leamington Spa and the surrounding south Warwickshire area. From his base in Coundon, Coventry, Leamington Spa is approximately 12 miles — a straightforward journey along the A45 or A46. He regularly works across:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="card p-5">
