            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Leamington town centre</strong> — Regency terraces, period conversions, and modern apartments</li>
              <li><strong>Milverton</strong> — Victorian terraces and semis north of the town</li>
              <li><strong>Lillington</strong> — post-war and inter-war residential, largely semi-detached</li>
              <li><strong>Sydenham</strong> — mixed residential east of the centre</li>
