              <li><strong>Cubbington</strong> — traditional village housing north-east of the town</li>
              <li><strong>Whitnash</strong> — residential area south of Leamington town centre</li>
              <li><strong>Warwick</strong> — historic market town immediately adjacent, also covered</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
